e name of Ms. C. Vanlalhriati has been used as money mule account and cheating, but, the subject Ms. C. Vanlalhriai was not involved in the operation </p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\">Enclosed :  1) Statement of Ms. C. Vanlalhriati</p> <p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">2) Bank Account Statement</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"></p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\">Yours faithfully,</p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\"></p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\"></p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\"></p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\"></p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\">(LALRINAWMA)</p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\">Addl. Superintendent of Police</p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\">CID (SB), Mizoram, Aizawl</p> <p style=\"margin-left:384px; text-align:left\"></p></p>'),
